<h4 id="2-2-2-tХ╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗">2-2-2. TХ╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗О╪ </h4>

<p>Б─▀	Е°╗Ф∙╟Е╜≈Г■╣Х╥╞Д╦╜О╪▄Е▐╕Д╦─Г╖█Г╖╟Д╦╨TФ┬√ToggleГ └Х╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗Г■╗Д╨▌Е╝·Г▌╟Ф≈╤И▓÷Е┬├И╒▒Е≥╗Г■╣Х╥╞Ц─┌Е╝┐Е▐╞Г■╗Д╨▌Е╟├Х╬⌠Е┘╔Д©║Е▐╥И╒▒Г▌┤Е▐≤Д╦╨Е▌÷Ф²╔Г └1/2.Е╕┌Ф·°Г╨╖Х│■nД╦╙TХ╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗О╪▄Е┬≥Ф≈╤И▓÷Е┬├И╒▒Д╦╨Е▌÷Ф²╔Г └(1/2)^nЦ─┌ TХ╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗Е┘╥Ф°┴TХ╬⌠Е┘╔О╪┬Ф∙╟Ф█╝О╪┴О╪▄Ф≈╤И▓÷Х╬⌠Е┘╔О╪▄Д╩╔Е▐┼Е▐╞И─┴Г └Е╓█Д╫█Е▓▄Д╫©Х┐╫Ф▌╖Е┬╤Д©║Е▐╥Ц─┌</p>

<div class="language-verilog highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">module</span> <span class="n">clock_divider_behavior</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">input</span> <span class="n">Clk</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">output</span> <span class="kt">reg</span> <span class="n">Q</span><span class="p">);</span> 
