<p>Б─▀	TХ╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗Х©≤Е▐╞Д╩╔Е┘╥Ф°┴Г╖╟Д╦╨CEО╪┬Ф≈╤И▓÷Д╫©Х┐╫О╪┴Г └Ф▌╖Е┬╤Д©║Е▐╥О╪▄Е┘╤Е╟├Е┘│Х╝╦Ф≈╤И▓÷Е┬├И╒▒Д╩┘Е°╗Е┘╤Ф≈╤И▓÷Х╬╧Ф╡©Ф≈╤Е▐▒Г■÷Ц─┌ Д╩╔Д╦▀Д╩ёГ═│Ф╗║Ф▀÷Д╨├TХ╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗Г └Е┼÷Х┐╫О╪▄Х╞╔Х╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗Е╞╧Ф≈╤И▓÷Г └Д╦▀И≥█Ф╡©Ф∙▐Ф└÷О╪▄Е╧╤Е┘╥Ф°┴Д╫▌Г■╣Е╧ЁФ°┴Ф∙┬Е╓█Д╫█Е▓▄И╚≤Г■╣Е╧ЁФ°┴Ф∙┬TФ▌╖Е┬╤Д©║Е▐╥Ц─┌</p>

<div class="language-verilog highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">module</span> <span class="n">T_ff_enable_behavior</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">input</span> <span class="n">Clk</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">input</span> <span class="n">reset_n</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">input</span> <span class="n">T</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">output</span> <span class="kt">reg</span> <span class="n">Q</span><span class="p">);</span> 
