</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Б─▀	Е╝·Г▌╟Е┤╨Ф²╔Г └RTLЕ▌÷Г░├Е⌡╬Е╕┌Д╦▀О╪ </p>

<figure><img class="docimage" src="images/simple_timing/271607238061109.jpg" alt="" /></figure>

<p>Б─▀	Х©≥Ф≤╞Е⌡═Д╦╨Е°╗Ф╞▐Д╦╙clkГ └Д╦┼Е█┤Ф╡©О╪▄Г■╣Х╥╞Е╧╤Е▐▒Е╝·Г▌╟Д╦╓Ф²║И²·И≤╩Е║·Х╣▀Е─╪Х╞╜Е▐╔О╪▄Ф┴─Д╩╔И°─Х╕│Д╦╓Д╦╙DХ╖╕Е▐▒Е≥╗Ц─┌</p>

<p>Б─▀	Х─▄Д╦▀И²╒Г └Д╬▀Е╜░Е▓▄Д╦┼Д╦╙Д╬▀Е╜░Е┤═Д╧▌Е╝▄Е┘╗Д╦─Ф═╥О╪▄Е▐╙Ф≤╞Ф┼┼И²·И≤╩Е║·Х╣▀Е─╪Ф■╧Ф┬░Д╨├И≤╩Е║·Х╣▀Е─╪О╪▄Е╕┌Д╦▀О╪ </p>

<div class="language-verilog highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">module</span> <span class="n">blocking</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">input</span> <span class="n">clk</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">input</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="kt">output</span> <span class="kt">reg</span> <span class="n">c</span><span class="p">);</span> 
